---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Chill-Dogs — a simple, focused resource for cooling and relaxation products that help keep dogs comfortable.">
  <section class="about container">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>About Chill-Dogs</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to Chill-Dogs — a simple, focused resource for dog parents who want practical products that support their dog's comfort.
      </p>
      <p>
        We created Chill-Dogs to make it easier to find reliable cooling and relaxation products without sorting through thousands of options online. Instead of covering everything in the pet world, we focus on two areas:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cooling products for warm days</li>
        <li>Relaxation products for high-energy moments</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <h3>Cooling</h3>
      <p>
        Warm weather can be tough on dogs. We highlight products designed to help them stay more comfortable, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cooling mats and elevated beds</li>
        <li>Lightweight cooling vests and bandanas</li>
        <li>Water play options</li>
        <li>Freezable toys and treat solutions</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These are everyday tools that can make summer outings and backyard time more manageable.
      </p>

      <h3>Relaxation</h3>
      <p>
        Some situations call for a calmer environment. We curate products that many dog owners use during:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Thunderstorms</li>
        <li>Fireworks</li>
        <li>Travel</li>
        <li>Time alone at home</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This may include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Compression wraps</li>
        <li>Relaxation-support chews</li>
        <li>Comfort-focused bedding</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="how-we-choose">How We Choose Products</h2>
      <p>
        We prioritize quality, durability, and strong customer feedback. Every recommendation fits within our two core themes — cooling and calming.
      </p>
      <p>
        We use affiliate links to support the site. If you purchase through our links, we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. This does not affect which products we choose to feature.
      </p>
      <p>
        Chill-Dogs is simply about helping you find straightforward solutions for keeping your dog comfortable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
